{"abstract":[{"text":"Handles push notification registration failure.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handlepushregistrationfailure:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSError","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"error"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The NSError received from APNs registration failure","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"error"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Call this method from your AppDelegate’s ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"application:didFailToRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithError:"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to notify Pushwoosh about registration failures.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This allows Pushwoosh to:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Log the error for debugging"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Retry registration if appropriate","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Update device status in the Control Panel","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Example","level":2,"text":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Handle registration failure with user feedback:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["class AppDelegate: UIResponder, UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func application(_ application: UIApplication,","                    didFailToRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithError error: Error) {","","        \/\/ Forward to Pushwoosh","        Pushwoosh.configure.handlePushRegistrationFailure(error as NSError)","","        \/\/ Log for debugging","        Logger.error(\"Push registration failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","","        \/\/ Handle specific error cases","        let nsError = error as NSError","        switch nsError.code {","        case 3010:","            \/\/ Simulator or push not supported","            Logger.warning(\"Push notifications not supported on this device\")","","        default:","            \/\/ Track error in analytics","            Analytics.track(\"push_registration_failed\", properties: [","                \"error_code\": nsError.code,","                \"error_message\": nsError.localizedDescription","            ])","","            \/\/ Optionally notify user","            if shouldShowPushError {","                showPushRegistrationError()","            }","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}]}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"title":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)handlePushRegistrationFailure:"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handlePushRegistrationFailure:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","title":"PWConfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/handlePushRegistrationFailure:":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handlepushregistrationfailure:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Handles push notification registration failure."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handlePushRegistrationFailure:","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:"}]}}}